GroupDocs.Annotation is essentially devised to add annotations in documents within a .NET applications. API comes with an extensive number of markup tools. These tools permit users to highlight, strikeout, and comment on text and images. This doesn't end up here user can avail numerous properties to control annotation's appearance in the document.
        
GroupDocs.Annotation supports a wide range of annotations. Following is the list of supported annotation types:

* Text
* Area
* Point
* TextStrikeout
* Polyline
* TextField
* Watermark
* TextReplacement
* Arrow
* TextRedaction
* ResourcesRedaction
* TextUnderline
* Distance

For more details on the library, please visit GroupDocs website at:
http://groupdocs.com/products/annotation/net

Note: The library comes up with some limitations in the evaluation mode. In order to test full features of GroupDocs.Annotation for .NET library, please request a free 30-day temporary license.
